<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #F7F3E3;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #EAE0CC;
        }

        .rounded-corners {
            border-radius: 15px;
        }

        .btn-custom {
            background-color: #3E3B2C;
            color: #FFF;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .btn-custom:hover {
            background-color: #2e2a20;
        }

        .feature-box {
            background-color: #D7CAB8;
            color: #3E3B2C;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            border-radius: 15px;
        }
        .footer {
        background-color: #F7F3E3; 
        color: #3E3B2C; 
        border-top: 3px solid #EAE0CC; 
    }

    .footer a {
        color: #3E3B2C; 
    }

    .footer a:hover {
        color: #2e2a20;
    }
    .full-height-section {
    min-height: 100vh; 
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center; 
    justify-content: center; 
}


    </style>
    <title>ILÊMI - Construa sua planta</title>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="header p-3">
        <img src="/public/logoilemi-preto.png" alt="Logotipo ILÊMI" height="60">
    </header>

    <div class="container mt-5 full-height-section">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-12 col-md-8 text-center">
                <h1>Bem vindo ao ILÊMI</h1>
                <p class="lead text-muted">Comece a gerar plantas baixas de forma descomplicada</p>
                <a href="/editor" class="btn btn-custom mt-3">Começar</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container  full-height-section">
        <h2 class="text-center mb-4">Possibilidades</h2>
        <div class="row text-center">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="feature-box rounded-corners">
                    <h3>Feature 1</h3>
                    <p>Crie seu próprio layout para habitação.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="feature-box rounded-corners">
                    <h3>Feature 2</h3>
                    <p>Veja alterações em tempo real.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="feature-box rounded-corners">
                    <h3>Feature 3</h3>
                    <p>Exporte seu layout em diversos formatos.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="footer bg-light text-center py-3 mt-4">
        <div class="container">
            <span>Criado por <a href="https://github.com/PedroThiagoRoque" target="_blank">Pedro Thiago Roque</a></span>
        </div>
    </footer>


<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
